-left\">\n                                        <h2>Amrutini.</h2>\n                                        <p class=\"green_blur_text\">Strengthen • Repair • Plump</p>\n                                        <p>A high-performance skincare line with the ambition to strengthen, the Amrutini range includes our Precious Potion, Transforming Serum &amp Luminosity Dewdrops. Journey through India’s East with this protein-rich collection that celebrates the hills in its heart and paints a vibrant picture that brings joy and resilience.</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-md-4 offset-md-4 col-6\">\n                                    <div class=\"srp-slider-right\">\n                                        <div class=\"kolkata-lady\">\n                                            <picture>\n                                                <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"{{ 'discover-the-collection-kolkata-lady.png' | file_url }}\" />\n                                                <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"{{ 'discover-the-collection-kolkata-lady-ipad.png' | file_url }}\" /> \n                                                <img src=\"{{ 'discover-the-collection-kolkata-lady-mobile-new.png' | file_url }}\" data-src=\"{{ 'discover-the-collection-kolkata-lady-mobile-new.png' | file_url }}\" alt=\"kolkata stamp\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" />\n                                            </picture>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <h2 class=\"love-h2\">With love from,</h2>\n                                        <h3>The Darjeeling Hills,</h3>\n                                        <h3>Bengal &amp; Assam</h3>\n                                        <picture>\n                                            <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-text.png\" />\n                                            <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-text-ipad.png\" /> \n                                            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-text-mobile-new.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-text-mobile-new.png\" alt=\"Amrutitni Sign\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive strong-text\" />\n                                        </picture>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"srp-slider-middle-image\">\n                        <div class=\"srp-slider-middle-image-shape\">\n                            <picture>\n                                <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider-middle.png\" />\n                                <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider-middle-ipad.png\" /> \n                                <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider-middle-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider-middle-mobile.png\" alt=\"Middle Hexagone\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" />\n                            </picture>\n                        </div>\n                        <!-- <div class=\"hover01 column\">\n                                <picture><img src=\"https://picsum.photos/300/200?image=244\"></picture>\n                            </div> -->\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"wakeup-sec pos-relative\">\n                <div class=\"container\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-md-5 offset-md-5 col-6 offset-6\">\n                            <div class=\"wakeup-sec-inner\">\n                                <p>Wake up to the warmth of the Precious Potion Vital Cream just as you would to the gentle rays of a golden sun. Soak up the morning mist just as the leaves would with the Luminosity Dewdrops. Feel the cool, crisp winds brush past you, as the True Brew Transforming Serum caresses your skin.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"true-water-cream\">\n                    <picture>\n                        <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-true-water-cream.png?v=1606112819\" /> \n                        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-true-water-cream-mobile-new.png?v=1606112818\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-true-water-cream-mobile-new.png?v=1606112818\" alt=\"True Water Cream\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" />\n                    </picture>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"purple-symbol\">\n                    <picture>\n                        <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-purple-symbol.png\" /> \n                        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-purple-symbol-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-purple-symbol-mobile.png\" alt=\"Purple\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" />\n                    </picture>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"purple-symbol-text\">\n                    <p>Symbols in this collection</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"night-slider\">\n                <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-md-10 offset-md-2\">\n                            <div class=\"ovr-hid\">\n                                <div class=\"owl-carousel owl-theme the_velvet-slider\">\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Night of the Full Moon</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider1.png?v=1606112155\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider1-ipad.png?v=1606112155\" /> \n                                                    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider1-mobile.png?v=1606112155\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider1-mobile.png?v=1606112155\" alt=\"Night of the Full Moon\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" />\n                                                </picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Night of the Full Moon</h2>\n                                                <p>Amrutini features a tea so precious; it is only plucked on clear, full moon nights, taking its cue from the celestial calendar. It is believed that the air’s high oxygen content and cosmic confluence during a full moon produces optimal harvest conditions. The Silver Tips Imperial tea, from the iconic Makaibari estate, nestled in Darjeeling’s vast blanket of emerald-green plantations, is certainly leaf and bud above the rest.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Ashwagandha</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider2.png?v=1606112532\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider2-ipad.png?v=1606112531\" /> \n                                                    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider2-mobile.png?v=1606112531\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider2-mobile.png?v=1606112531\" alt=\"Ashwagandha\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image carouser-image-slider2\" />\n                                                </picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Ashwagandha</h2>\n                                                <p class=\"slider2-p\">Ashwagandha (Indian Ginseng) is a whisper of the past and holds the magic of the future. Extracted from the roots of the plant, this powerful herb is known to increase defense against diseases by improving cell-mediated immunity. It draws its name from the word Ashwa (horse), since it is believed to possess its namesakes’ strength and vitality.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Bengali Script</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider3.png?v=1606112651\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider3-ipad.png?v=1606112651\" /> \n                                                    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider3-mobile.png?v=1606112651\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider3-mobile.png?v=1606112651\" alt=\"Bengali Script\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" />\n                                                </picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Bengali Script</h2>\n                                                <p class=\"slider3-p\">In every corner of Bengal, there is a tale to tell. From the North, which touches the feet of the Himalayas, to the South, where the great Bay lies, nature’s beauty is abundant in this majestic and rich land. The cursive Bengali script is believed to have originated in the 10th century and is the medium for many acclaimed literary works. It is a befitting script for a land and language of such poetry.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Bridges &amp; Buildings</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider4.png\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider4-ipad.png\" /> \n                                                    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider4-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-slider4-mobile.png\" alt=\"Bridges &amp; Buildings\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" />\n                                                </picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Bridges &amp; Buildings</h2>\n                                                <p class=\"slider4-p\">New York’s structures are a symbol of human ingenuity, and a foundation of strength and stability. We take inspiration from many iconic structures- the Brooklyn Bridge, which has stood the test of time, and the Oculus, a brilliant exposition of design and technology. From old to new, we forge a path that brings together traditional elements with modern innovation.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"bottle-full\">\n                <div>\n                    <picture>\n                        <source media=\"(min-width:1352px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-bottle-full_28759e7e-1cc9-4526-9837-cd45f40d2499.png?v=1606111796\" />\n                        <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-bottle-full-ipad_1d8d5c4b-9a99-4a79-9ede-bee9fc19a6fd.png?v=1606111795\" /> \n                        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-bottle-full-mobile_27a6299a-ae69-41cd-9986-c70899a5c0d0.png?v=1606111797\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/discover-the-collection-bottle-full-mobile_27a6299a-ae69-41cd-9986-c70899a5c0d0.png?v=1606111797\" alt=\"Bottle Full\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" />\n                    </picture>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"diveinto-text\">\n                <div class=\"container\">\n                    <div class=\"diveinto-text-inner\">\n                        <p>Dive into a vibrant color palette as you uncover the collection and its packaging which has hues of blue, hints of green and rays of mustard. Experience the diverse artistry of Bengal with nuances of Kantha designs against the backdrop of New York.</p>\n                      <div class=\"buy-btn3\">\n                            <a href=\"/products/amrutini%C2%AE-collection\" class=\"product-buy-btn3\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Shop_Now_Button.png?v=1614355657\" width=\"150\"></a>\n                        </div>    <br/> \n                      <h2>Allow it all to come together in a design as bespoke as the mosaic of your memories.</h2>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
